Package: jamba
Title: Just Analysis Methods Base
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person(given="James M.", family="Ward",
    email="jmw86069@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Jam base functions focused on bioinformatics.
    Efficient gene-centric alphanumeric sort,
    unique name version assignment, colorized console and HTML output,
    color ramp and palette manipulation,
    Rmarkdown cache import, styled Excel worksheet export,
    rasterized and interpolated smooth scatter and image plots,
    list to delimited vector, efficient list tools.
biocViews:
